  <entry>
    <title>【持续更新】Windows系统实用bat命令大全</title>
    <link href="https://blog.w6wg.cn/1/"/>
    <id>https://blog.w6wg.cn/1/</id>
    <published>2022-01-02T09:08:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-08-15T08:21:21.232Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="一、服务类"><a href="#一、服务类" class="headerlink" title="一、服务类"></a>一、服务类</h4><h5 id="启动系统服务命令"><a href="#启动系统服务命令" class="headerlink" title="启动系统服务命令"></a>启动系统服务命令</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@echo off</span><br><span class="line">net start 服务名称</span><br><span class="line">exit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="结束系统服务命令"><a href="#结束系统服务命令" class="headerlink" title="结束系统服务命令"></a>结束系统服务命令</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@echo off</span><br><span class="line">net stop 服务名称</span><br><span class="line">exit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="结束并重启服务命令"><a href="#结束并重启服务命令" class="headerlink" title="结束并重启服务命令"></a>结束并重启服务命令</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@echo off</span><br><span class="line">echo STOP</span><br><span class="line">net stop 服务名称</span><br><span class="line">timeout 5</span><br><span class="line">echo START</span><br><span class="line">net start 服务名称</span><br><span class="line">pause</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>timeout 5</code> 表示等待5秒后再打开服务</p><h5 id="设置服务启动类型"><a href="#设置服务启动类型" class="headerlink" title="设置服务启动类型"></a>设置服务启动类型</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@echo off</span><br><span class="line">sc config 服务名称 start= auto（自动）/demand（手动）/disabled（禁用）</span><br><span class="line">exit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="二、关闭exe程序"><a href="#二、关闭exe程序" class="headerlink" title="二、关闭exe程序"></a>二、关闭exe程序</h4><h5 id="强制关闭程序"><a href="#强制关闭程序" class="headerlink" title="强制关闭程序"></a>强制关闭程序</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">taskkill /f /im RaiDrive.exe</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>RaiDrive.exe</code>是程序名称</p><h5 id="强制关闭所有程序"><a href="#强制关闭所有程序" class="headerlink" title="强制关闭所有程序"></a>强制关闭所有程序</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">taskkill /F /FI &quot;USERNAME eq 账户名&quot; /FI &quot;IMAGENAME ne explorer.exe&quot; /FI &quot;IMAGENAME ne dwm.exe</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="三、关机、重启"><a href="#三、关机、重启" class="headerlink" title="三、关机、重启"></a>三、关机、重启</h4><h5 id="关机、重启"><a href="#关机、重启" class="headerlink" title="关机、重启"></a>关机、重启</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">shutdown -s -t 10</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>-s（关机）<br>-r（重启）<br>10（10秒后关机）</p><h4 id="四、删除文件"><a href="#四、删除文件" class="headerlink" title="四、删除文件"></a>四、删除文件</h4><h5 id="删除文件夹下所有文件"><a href="#删除文件夹下所有文件" class="headerlink" title="删除文件夹下所有文件"></a>删除文件夹下所有文件</h5><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">del C:\Users\1\AppData\Local\Temp\*.* /f/s/q/a pause</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>待更新…</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
